                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000917-99-victim954 t18000917-99-viclabel536"></join>; my wife is a worker of muslin shawls, at <placeName id="t18000917-99-crimeloc537">Hoxton</placeName>
