               <p>JAMES WILLIAMSON sworn. - I am servant to Mr. Dexter, Whitechapel-road, (produces three shawls, and a yard of muslin); I cannot say who it was that I took them in of; the prisoner used frequently to come to the shop.</p>
               <p>Q. Look at the duplicates produced by Ray, and say if they are your's? - A. They are.(The property was deposed to by Mrs. Grant).</p>
               <p>The prisoner did not say any thing in her defence.</p>
